#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:2
msgid "The Blockchain without The Bitcoin"
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:4
msgid "bitcoindesigned.com"
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:6
msgid ""
"A little more on the idea that “the real technology is the Blockchain, we "
"should implement it without this silly Bitcoin”."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:8
msgid "First things first - in very simple words"
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:10
msgid "What is Bitcoin (with capital B)?"
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:12
msgid ""
"It’s a protocol for a decentralized peer-to-peer network that creates "
"consensus without needing a central authority to provide trust."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:14
msgid "What is bitcoin (with lowercase b)?"
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:16
msgid "The currency  (token) issued in the mining process."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:18
msgid "What is the blockchain?"
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:20
msgid ""
"It’s the public ledger where the network records (transactions) are written."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:22
msgid "How does it work?"
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:24
msgid ""
"Nodes verify and propagate transactions while miners gain permission to "
"write new blocks in it."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:26
msgid "How do miners do it?"
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:28
msgid ""
"Solving mathematical problems using a lot of processing power (read hardware "
"and electricity costs)."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:30
msgid "Why do they do it?"
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:32
msgid ""
"Because their investment of time and resources is rewarded with bitcoins ("
"currently 12.5 BTC per block mined)."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:34
msgid "Isn’t it like a database?"
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:36
msgid ""
"It has the idea of a database, but one that’s decentralized and still "
"guarantees consensus and that the entries are true."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:38
msgid "Why can we truste it?"
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:40
msgid "Because math neither lies nor has political or economic interests."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:42
msgid "Why don’t they do bad stuff to make more money?"
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:44
msgid ""
"Because Bitcoin uses Games Theory and incentives to make it more profitable "
"to be honest."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:46
msgid "Now that we settled that, we can start imagining…"
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:48
msgid ""
"Ok, you want the blockchain but not bitcoins (or any other token with value)."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:50
msgid "And you need miners to write your new blocks."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:52
msgid "That leaves 2 scenarios:"
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:54
msgid "If you are imagining decentralized mining (like in Bitcoin)."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:56
msgid ""
"You are automatically supposing the miners are going to spend time and money "
"just for fun or for the goodness in their hearts."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:58
msgid "Sorry, that’s not very likely."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:60
msgid ""
"If you know people won’t mine without an incentive (that’s a good start)."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:62
msgid ""
"You will mine for your own (in your company, institution or other entity "
"that chooses to use the blockchain)."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:64
msgid "Congratulations! You’ve just created a slow database."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:66
msgid "Conclusions"
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:68
msgid ""
"The blockchain is pretty inefficient (slow and resource-consuming) if used "
"just for registering information without a token with value."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:70
msgid ""
"The amount of resources “wasted” in mining only makes sense because it "
"allows a decentralized and authority-free security."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:72
msgid "In other words... (though not considering many technical aspects)"
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:74
msgid "When you say:"
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:76
msgid "Bitcoin is nothing, the real technology is the Blockchain."
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:78
msgid "It sounds as logical as:"
msgstr ""

#: ./the-blockchain-without-the-bitcoin/source-text.txt:80
msgid "This Internet is nothing, the really cool thing it’s HTML!"
msgstr ""

